lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>Click an icon to open a list=
. Click
the icon again to close it, or use the close icon at top right of the list.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>E=
ach list
can be scrolled up and down by clicking on the arrows at top and bottom, or=
 by
using the mouse scroll wheel while hovered over the list.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=3D"Picture_x0020_3" o:s=
pid=3D"_x0000_s1027"
